{"statement":{"language":"es","images":[],"sources":[],"markdown":"# Descripci\u00f3n\nLa siguiente recurrencia para $n = 2^k$ tiene una soluci\u00f3n exacta de la forma $\\sum_{i=0}^{t}(u^iw) + x^yz$ obtenida mediante la t\u00e9cnica de sustituci\u00f3n repetida.\n\n - Si $n=1$ entonces $T(1) = c$\n - Si $n>1$ entonces $T(n) = aT(\\frac{n}{2}) + b$.\n\nEscribe un programa que, dados los valores de $a, b, c$ y $n$, determine los valores de $t, u, w, x, y, z$ que correspondan con el patr\u00f3n obtenido por sustituci\u00f3n repetida.\n\n# Entrada\nCuatro enteros $a, b, c, n$. Puedes suponer que $0 \\leq a, b, c, n \\leq 1000$ y que $n = 2^k$ con $k \\geq 0$.\n\n# Salida\nSeis enteros $t, u, w, x, y, z$.\n\n# Ejemplo\n||input\n1 1 1 1\n||output\n-1 1 1 1 0 1\n||end\n"},"settings":{"cases":{"statement_001":{"in":"1 1 1 1","out":"-1 1 1 1 0 1","weight":1}},"limits":{"ExtraWallTime":"0s","MemoryLimit":33554432,"OutputLimit":10240,"OverallWallTimeLimit":"1m0s","TimeLimit":"1s"},"validator":{"name":"custom","tolerance":1.0e-9,"custom_validator":{"source":"","language":"cpp"}}},"problem_id":11205,"title":"Resolviendo una recurrencia","alias":"Resolviendo-una-recurrencia","input_limit":10240,"visits":0,"submissions":93,"accepted":48,"difficulty":1.9385136542461852,"creation_date":1590426399,"source":"UAM Azcapotzalco 2020","order":"normal","visibility":2,"email_clarifications":false,"allow_user_add_tags":false,"show_diff":"none","quality_seal":true,"version":"e3b115baf4b8eb6f07882483ea2d9513db5e12d1","commit":"e4f2f0785bfe1d0f3d4dbc69d3069c5a21292ced","nominationStatus":{"alreadyReviewed":false,"dismissed":false,"dismissedBeforeAc":false,"nominated":false,"nominatedBeforeAc":false,"language":"","canNominateProblem":false,"solved":false,"tried":false},"problemsetter":{"username":"rcc","classname":"user-rank-international-master","name":"rcc","creation_date":1590426399},"languages":["c11-gcc","c11-clang","cpp11-gcc","cpp11-clang","cpp17-gcc","cpp17-clang","java","py2","py3","r